==English==
===Etymology===
From ''good'' meaning ''[[holy]]''
===Noun phrase===
'''[[good|Good]] [[Friday]]'''

#The [[Friday]] before [[Easter Sunday]], believed by [[Christian]]s to be the day on which [[Christ]] was [[crucified]].

